          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "content",
          "source": "Defining a simple and-rule in standard technical language : A is true - if B,C and D are true \n\n---\n\nA [B, C, D]\n",
          "target": "使用标准技术语言定义一个简单的“与”规则：如果 B、C 和 D 为真，则 A 为真\\n\\n---\\n\\nA [B, C, D]\\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "content",
          "source": "If you don't want to reuse some symbols with in different rule, it it possible to define groups which will be inserted in rules instead of the groups name\n\n---\n\nMyGroup ~ Elem1, Elem2, Elem3 ~\nMyOptions 1|1 {MyGroup}\n",
          "target": "如果不想在不同规则中重复使用某些符号，可以定义组，这些组将被插入规则中，而不是组名\\n\\n---\\n\\nMyGroup ~ Elem1, Elem2, Elem3 ~\\nMyOptions 1|1 {MyGroup}\\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "content",
          "source": "It is possible to cascade rule only by using same symbolname for a new rule : \nA is true - if B or C is true; \nB is true - if B1 or B2 is true\n C is true - if C1 and C2 are true \n\n---\n\nA [B, C]\nB {B1 , B2}\nC [C1 , C2]",
          "target": "可以通过对新规则使用相同的符号名称来级联规则：\\n如果 B 或 C 为真，则 A 为真；\\n如果 B1 或 B2 为真，则 B 为真\\n如果 C1 和 C2 为真，则 C 为真\\n\\n---\\n\\nA [B, C]\\nB {B1 , B2}\\nC [C1 , C2]"
        },
